    ## Icons
    Application Icons are an icon font titled [FontAwesome](http://fontawesome.io). The font files are stored in the `/icon-fonts` directory and they are accesed by a Sass mixin `@include icon-font($fa-variable);`. Some examples of icons are listed below with their variable names. All the variable names follow a convention without the `fa-` prefix. You can find all the variables defined in the `_font-awesome.scss` file and [see examples of all the icons here](http://fontawesome.io/icons/).

    <em class="highlighter">Also to note:</em> there are over 500 icons in this library. The lilelyhood of any application needing all of them is pretty slim. Right now, icons that are in buttons, styles live in `_buttons.scss`. If we need generic icon classes, the should live in `_font-awesome.scss` where you can find the icon variables listed.

